Articles.Content:
Hello! Thought I'd just share the new series I'm working on, and see if I could get some feedback. I'll have a lot more time (now that its summer) to make these videos, and I'd like some critical commentary on where I can improve. These are the first youtube videos I've ever made, so give them a chance, and let me know what you think !

Project Duna

Thanks in advance for all of you who end up watching some of it!
